Perfect. Portrait + wrong position. The root cause is almost certainly a coordinate space mismatch between ML Kit and ARCore. ML Kit returns bounding boxes in **image coordinates** (which in portrait mode are rotated 90° relative to screen coordinates), but we're feeding them directly as screen coordinates to ARCore's hit-test. Here's the complete fix with full debug overlay:

